    "path": "src/agent/task",
    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime. Task drives the per-task worker thread: it sends the initial status, triggers the initial plan through Step, and routes task, step, execution, and placeholder plan events, delegating step routing to Step. TaskState stores session context, plan_queue, execution_map from ExecutionSignature to StepSignature, and the step WorkQueue (step numbers derive from the queue size) with a manual Debug impl. task_execution.rs starts execution steps, records execution_map entries, maps succeeding execution status back into StepEvent::Complete via Step, and starts execution-analysis plans from completed execution output.",
